PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772478696
OL,3,CCancelled flights and closed airspace:
OL,4,CHow Iran war has sparked travel chaos
OL,6,FThe British government believes
OL,7,Fhundreds of thousands of UK citizens
OL,8,Fare in the region, and is now drawing
OL,9,Fup plans to evacuate them.
OL,11,FThis has led to the airspace in the
OL,12,Fworld's most important travel hubs
OL,13,Fbeing closed for the foreseeable
OL,14,Ffuture. About half a million
OL,15,Fpassengers use airports in Dubai, Doha
OL,16,For Abu Dhabi each day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772478696
OL,3,CCancelled flights and closed airspace:
OL,4,CHow Iran war has sparked travel chaos
OL,6,FPresident Donald Trump has said their
OL,7,Foperation is "ahead of schedule", but
OL,8,Fhe has not laid out what his exact
OL,9,Fhopes are for the conflict, and he has
OL,10,Falso said he is prepared to keep
OL,11,Foperations going for a long time if
OL,12,Fnecessary.
OL,14,FIran and its regional allies, like
OL,15,FHezbollah, are also likely to carry on
OL,16,Fretaliating as long as they are being
OL,17,Fattacked.
OL,19,FIf the situation worsens, the UK may
OL,20,Fhave to begin one of the biggest
OL,21,Fevacuations since World War Two.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
