OL,3,CCancelled flights and closed airspace:
OL,4,CHow Iran war has sparked travel chaos
OL,6,FHow many UK nationals are in the Gulf?
OL,8,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper told
OL,9,FGood Morning Britain she believes
OL,10,Fthere are around 300,000 Brits in the
OL,11,FGulf nations who have been targeted by
OL,12,FIran.
OL,14,FThey include Bahrain, Israel, Kuwait,
OL,15,FPalestine, Qatar and the United Arab
OL,16,FEmirates (UAE).
OL,18,FOut of those nations, the UAE is
OL,19,Fbelieved to have the most Brits spread
OL,20,Fbetween Dubai and Abu Dhabi.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
