OL,3,CCancelled flights and closed airspace:
OL,4,CHow Iran war has sparked travel chaos
OL,6,FEveryone in the region has been
OL,7,Fencouraged to register their presence
OL,8,Fwith the local British embassy in case
OL,9,Fan evacuation needs to be organised.
OL,11,FCooper has said around 104,000 Brits
OL,12,Fhave done this so far.
OL,14,FThe government has used the
OL,15,Fregistration scheme before to provide
OL,16,Furgent updates to people affected by
OL,17,Finternational crises, but it has not
OL,18,Fpreviously needed to deal with so many
OL,19,Fpeople in so many different countries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
