OL,3,CCancelled flights and closed airspace:
OL,4,CHow Iran war has sparked travel chaos
OL,6,FBritish nationals are being advised to
OL,7,Ffollow the instructions of local
OL,8,Fauthorities and monitor the Foreign
OL,9,FOffice's travel advice, which
OL,10,Fofficials expect to change rapidly.
OL,12,FNo concrete information has been
OL,13,Freleased about what will happen if an
OL,14,Fevacuation is ordered.
OL,16,FUK-based aviation consultant John
OL,17,FStrickland said the disruption was
OL,18,F"pretty unprecedented".
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
