OL,3,CCancelled flights and closed airspace:
OL,4,CHow Iran war has sparked travel chaos
OL,6,FHe said: "The Gulf carriers are now so
OL,7,Ffundamental to much of global
OL,8,Faviation, not least east-west flows
OL,9,Fbetween Europe and Asia.
OL,11,F"I can't recall a situation ` other
OL,12,Fthan the pandemic ` where we've had
OL,13,Fthese Gulf hubs out of action in this
OL,14,Fway before.
OL,16,F"We've had other conflicts in the
OL,17,Fregion, but not, I think, really in
OL,18,Fthe scale of military conflict or
OL,19,Fscale of activity that we have now
OL,20,Fwith the Gulf carriers."
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@AOUxD@AOU|D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
