OL,3,CCancelled flights and closed airspace:
OL,4,CHow Iran war has sparked travel chaos
OL,6,FMr Strickland said "hundreds of
OL,7,Fthousands of people" in Dubai or other
OL,8,FMiddle Eastern hub airports "weren't
OL,9,Fsupposed to be there".
OL,11,FWhat's being done for stranded
OL,12,Fpassengers?
OL,14,FThe UAE is covering the food and
OL,15,Faccommodation costs of tens of
OL,16,Fthousands of travellers stranded in
OL,17,Fthe country.
OL,26,@nD@TOUoD@TO]pD@]OUqD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
