OL,3,CCancelled flights and closed airspace:
OL,4,CHow Iran war has sparked travel chaos
OL,6,FCNN reported the UAE's Department of
OL,7,FCulture and Tourism sent a notice to
OL,8,Fhotels requesting them to extend the
OL,9,Fstay of passengers who are unable to
OL,10,Ftravel "for reasons beyond their
OL,11,Fcontrol."
OL,13,FQatar has been offering similar
OL,14,Fsupport. X user Ershad Kaleebullah
OL,15,Fsaid he has been offered food coupons
OL,16,Fthat were valid at all food vendors in
OL,17,FDoha airport.
OL,19,FHe said he was later evacuated from
OL,20,Fthe airport and moved to a hotel along
OL,21,Fwith many other stranded passengers.
OL,26,@rD@HOUsD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
