OL,3,CCancelled flights and closed airspace:
OL,4,CHow Iran war has sparked travel chaos
OL,6,FWhat to do if your flight is cancelled?
OL,8,FAirspace closures in the Middle East
OL,9,Fhave resulted in commercial flights
OL,10,Fbeing grounded since the attacks began
OL,11,Fon Saturday.
OL,13,FNearly half of the flights scheduled
OL,14,Fto depart from London Heathrow to the
OL,15,Fregion on Sunday were cancelled.
OL,17,FQatar Airways, Etihad and Emirates
OL,18,Fhave all suspended flights from their
OL,19,Fhome bases.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
