OL,3,CCancelled flights and closed airspace:
OL,4,CHow Iran war has sparked travel chaos
OL,6,FBritish Airways and Virgin have also
OL,7,Fcancelled flights to the region. In
OL,8,Ftotal, thousands of flights have been
OL,9,Fcancelled.
OL,11,FIf your flight has been cancelled, it
OL,12,Fis best to contact your carrier and
OL,13,Fembassy.
OL,15,FThere have also been several stories
OL,16,Fof local governments offering support
OL,17,Fto stranded people.
OL,19,FIn a social media post, Etihad Airways
OL,20,Fsaid its customers should:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
