OL,3,CCancelled flights and closed airspace:
OL,4,CHow Iran war has sparked travel chaos
OL,6,FOther carriers are issuing similar
OL,7,Fadvice.
OL,9,FAre countries arranging repatriation
OL,10,Fflights?
OL,12,FWith the Gulf region being such an
OL,13,Fimportant part of the international
OL,14,Ftravel network, with numerous transit
OL,15,Fairports, business conferences and a
OL,16,Flarge tourism sector, many nations are
OL,17,Fstruggling with the same issue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
