OL,3,CCancelled flights and closed airspace:
OL,4,CHow Iran war has sparked travel chaos
OL,6,FIt is understood any repatriation of
OL,7,FUK nationals would likely be organised
OL,8,Fby the Foreign Office, with one
OL,9,Fpotential route involving people
OL,10,Ftravelling by land to Saudi Arabia
OL,11,Ffrom where they could board flights.
OL,13,FThe Civil Aviation Authority oversaw
OL,14,Fmass repatriations of customers
OL,15,Faffected by the collapse of travel
OL,16,Fcompanies Monarch and Thomas Cook as
OL,17,Fthey involved many holidaymakers
OL,18,Fprotected by the Atol scheme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
