OL,3,CCancelled flights and closed airspace:
OL,4,CHow Iran war has sparked travel chaos
OL,6,FOn Sunday, Germany admitted it was
OL,7,Fstruggling to arrange evacuations for
OL,8,Fits citizens in the area due to
OL,9,Fairspace closures.
OL,11,FThe EU is due to meet early this week
OL,12,Fto discuss whether it needs to
OL,13,Fcoordinate repatriation flights.
OL,15,FWill travel insurance cover any
OL,16,Fdisruption caused by the conflict?
OL,18,FThis will depend heavily on what your
OL,19,Ftravel insurance says.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
