OL,3,CCancelled flights and closed airspace:
OL,4,CHow Iran war has sparked travel chaos
OL,6,FMost travel insurers do offer cover
OL,7,Ffor travel disruption for some
OL,8,Funforeseen circumstance.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FBut Compare the Market says standard
OL,16,Ftravel insurance deals often do not
OL,17,Fcover acts of war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
