OL,3,CCancelled flights and closed airspace:
OL,4,CHow Iran war has sparked travel chaos
OL,6,FThey said: "Therefore, if you're
OL,7,Ftravelling to, or near, a war zone,
OL,8,Fyou need to take out specialist travel
OL,9,Finsurance and check that war is
OL,10,Fcovered. That way, if a war breaking
OL,11,Fout forces you to cancel, interrupt or
OL,12,Fdelay your trip, you can make a claim."
OL,14,FTravel insurance companies also do not
OL,15,Fusually offer insurance if you're
OL,16,Fplanning on entering a country that is
OL,17,Fcurrently under the Foreign Office's
OL,18,Fspecial do-not-travel guidance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
